            <div class="title">
                Nationalisation
            </div>

            <div class="right-arrow">
                    <a href="/Commons/1948-11-02/debates/63071a48-7f89-4fef-936c-be4a2ee32306/ControlOfPosters" class="next" title="Go to the next debate">
