                Mr. Sydney Silverman  (Nelson and Colne)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-7d1bd4b7-af40-4b80-91b6-4829ea668c06" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
