<p class="">Plans are being made whereby I hope and believe in a few years we shall see a rapid upward trend in the output and a rapid downward trend in the cost of production of coal in this country. The right hon. Gentleman also referred, in passing, to electricity and gas. My right hon. Friend the Minister for Fuel and Power is to speak——</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
