<p class="">Before the right hon. Gentleman leaves the question of coal may I remind him that I asked specifically whether we were to have the advantage of the publication not only of the Burrows report, but also of the evidence.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
