                Mr.maclay  (Montrose Burghs)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-6aa3cfdd-2e6b-4c7d-82d2-b7947d250bf7" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1948-11-02/debates/0117f708-07f5-4d01-b68b-f89f7066070a/Nationalisation#contribution-6aa3cfdd-2e6b-4c7d-82d2-b7947d250bf7">
