                Mr. Scollan  (Renfrew)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-8664980f-b9ba-41c8-94b0-5f14badf6b76" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
