<p class="">May I assist the hon. Gentleman's memory? One of the reasons why Sir Kingsley Wood did not say when this thing was going to be introduced was because he did not intend to go cap in hand and beg for American dollars to put it through.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-05cd2d76-1998-47ff-aed5-db93a67aa3e2" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
