<p class="">Does the hon. Gentleman think that this intricate machinery for reaching a decision would be as effective as the chairman of a board of directors of a private company, who can make a decision in a matter of hours?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
