    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">Is it not the case that the main idea of nationalisation is that the parasites should go out of business and the workers should get the fruits of their labours?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-30d570e3-c215-47a4-a6c2-3aec765368c2" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1948-11-02/debates/0117f708-07f5-4d01-b68b-f89f7066070a/Nationalisation#contribution-30d570e3-c215-47a4-a6c2-3aec765368c2">
