<p class="">I cannot accept that. I hope that we are examining this problem in the non-party spirit in which this Debate is inevitably conducted, because there is no disagreement between the two sides about nationalisation in principle. We are only disagreeing about the point where nationalisation stops.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
