    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">The hon. Gentleman's remarks are a distortion of what I said and he will not give way.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-1009e9a4-f7b5-4923-a8d0-f00ab09cd649" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
